#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about managing stress.\n"
"\n"
"We know how stressful it is to bring up teenagers in these times. Learning to manage your stress helps you – and your family."
msgstr ""
"Isihloko sanamhlanje simalunga nokulawula uxinzelelo.\n"
"\n"
"Siyayazi kunzima kangakanani na ukukhulisa abantwana abafikisayo kula amaxesha. Ukufunda ukulawula uxinzelelo lwakho kunceda wena - kunye nosapho lwakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can managing stress help you and your family? Tap play to find out"
msgstr "Ingaba ukulawula uxinzelelo kungakunceda wena nosapho lwakho? Cofa udlala ukufumanisa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is managing stress.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to know how to manage our stress. At times our children can behave in ways that make us feel stressed and us as parents can make our children feel stressed too.\n"
"\n"
"So, it is important to notice when we feel stressed and take a pause and breathe. That will help you manage your stress."
msgstr ""
"Molweni, nonke. \n"
"\n"
"Isihloko sanamhlanje kukulawula uxinzelelo. \n"
"\n"
"Kubalulekile ukwazi indlela yokulawula uxinzelelo lwethu. Ngamanye amaxesha abantwana bethu bangaziphatha ngeendlela ezinokusenza sizive sinoxinzelelo yaye nathi bazali sinokwenza abantwana bethu bazive benonxinzelelo nabo. \n"
"\n"
"Ngoko, kubalulekile ukuqaphela xa siziva sinoxinzelelo kwaye sime siphefumle. Loo nto iya kunceda ulawule uxinzelelo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"With a few small changes, you can feel more peaceful in your normal day-to-day life.\n"
"\n"
"When you are peaceful, your family members will get calmer too!"
msgstr ""
"Kutshintsho oluncinci, ungaziva unoxolo ngakumbi kubomi bakho besiqhelo bemihla ngemihla.\n"
"\n"
"Xa unoxolo, nosapho lwakho luyazola!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Pause, take a breath. Now hear how taking a simple pause helped @data.characters.media_female_4.name and her teens"
msgstr "Yima, phefumla. Ngoku mamela ukuba ukuma ithutyana kunceda njani u@data.characters.media_female_4.name kunye nabantwana bakhe abafikisayo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Life is tough sometimes. Before I joined @global.app_name, I used to be grumpy at all times. I would take out my anger on everyone at home, not only my teens but even my husband as well. They would run away when I came home because they knew I would start yelling at them.\n"
"\n"
"Learning to take a pause and breathe was difficult at first. But every time I tried it, it helped me to calm down. Now my teens are no longer running away when I come home and they actually listen better than when I used to shout at them!"
msgstr ""
"Ubomi bunzima ngamanye amaxesha. Phambi kokuba ndizibandakanye kwi @global.app_name, bendihlala ndinengcwangu ngalo lonke ixesha. Bendikhuphela umsindo wam kumntu wonke osekhayeni, ibingengobantwana bam bodwa kodwa nomyeni wam. Babebalekela kude xa ndifika ekhayeni kuba babeyazi ndizakubangxolisa.\n"
"\n"
"Ukufunda ukuma kwaye ndiphefumle bekunzima ekuqaleni. Kodwa ngalo lonke ixesha ndizama, yandinceda ndehlisa umoya. Ngoku abantwana bam abasabalekeli kude xa ndifika ekhayeni kwaye bamamela ngcono kunangexesha bendithethela phezulu nabo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s look at an example of how stress can sometimes just get too much, for all of us:"
msgstr "Makhe sijonge indlela uxinezeleko olunokuthi maxa wambi lube ngaphaya kwamandla, kuthi sonke:"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name lost his job. He was sitting at home feeling frustrated and stressed when @data.characters.f1_son_18.name entered the room."
msgstr "u@data.characters.f1_father.name uphelelwe ngumsebenzi. Ebehleli endlini eziva ekhathazekile kwaye enoxinzelelo xa u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name engena egumbini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Leave me alone and mind your own business!"
msgstr "Yohlukana nam kwaye hoya umsebenzi wakho!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What did I do? You never listen!"
msgstr "Yintoni endiyenzileyo? Zange wamamela!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I said leave me alone or you will get a beating!"
msgstr "Ndithe yohlukana nam okanye uzakubethwa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look! I have made a house!"
msgstr "Jonga! Ndenze indlu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Who cares about your stupid house!"
msgstr "Ngubani oyikhathaleleyo londlu yobudenge yakho!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about what happened in this story."
msgstr "Makhe sicinge malunga nokwenzekileyo kweli bali."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name's
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you think @data.characters.f1_father.name's son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, felt?"
msgstr "Ucinga ukuba unyana ka@data.characters.f1_father.name, u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name waziva njani?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, he did not understand why his father, @data.characters.f1_father.name, got angry, and probably felt all these emotions."
msgstr "Ewe, khange ayiqonde ukuba kutheni utata wakhe, u@data.characters.f1_father.name, wabanomsindo, kwaye azive zonke ezimvakalelo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And @data.characters.f1_father.name?"
msgstr "Kwaye @data.characters.f1_father.name?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sad"
msgstr "Ulusizi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Scared"
msgstr "Usoyika"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Confused"
msgstr "Ubhidekile"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Angry"
msgstr "Unomsindo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly. @data.characters.f1_father.name was in a difficult situation and this argument only made things worse."
msgstr "Ngokwenene. U@data.characters.f1_father.name wayekwimeko enzima kwaye oluxambuliswano lwenza izinto zanzima ngakumbi."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you for thinking along! Let’s go back in time and see what @data.characters.f1_father.name does now:"
msgstr "Enkosi ngokucinga kunye! Masibuyele emva ngexesha kwaye sibone ukuba u@data.characters.f1_father.name wenzani ngoku:"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name lost his job. He was sitting at home feeling frustrated and stressed, when his son @data.characters.f1_son_18.name entered the room."
msgstr "u@data.characters.f1_father.name uphelelwe ngumsebenzi. Ebehleli endlini eziva ekhathazekile kwaye enoxinzelelo xa u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name engena egumbini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can I have money to buy some airtime?"
msgstr "Ndingakwazi ukufumana imali yokuthenga airtime?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*(taking a breath)* I’m sorry son. I had a difficult day today. The boss fired me."
msgstr "*(ephefumlo)* Uxolo nyana. Bendinemini enzima namhlanje. Umphathi wam undigxothile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh no! I need a new school uniform."
msgstr "Oh hayi! Ndidinga impahla entsha yesikolo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I’ll try, son, and your @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name's job will help us get by while I look for another job."
msgstr "Ndizakuzama, nyana, kwaye umsebenzi ka @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name uzakusinceda ngethuba ndisakhangela omnye umsebenzi."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Should I also help you look for work, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name?"
msgstr "Nam ndingancedisa ukukukhangelisa umsebenzi, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No it’s okay, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. I appreciate your offer. The most important thing is that you work hard at school. Thanks for listening to me."
msgstr "Hayi kulungile, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. Ndiyakwamkela ukuzinikela kwakho. Eyonanto ibalulekileyo kukuba usebenze nzima esikolweni. Enkosi ngokundimamela."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s play some soccer together. It will help me get this stress off my mind for a bit."
msgstr "Masidlale ibhola ekhatywayo sobabini. Izakundinceda ndikhuphe uxinzelelo olusengqondweni yam oko mzuzwana."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name!"
msgstr "Kulungile, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are a few skills to help you manage stress that you can use with your teens!"
msgstr "Nazi izakhono ezimbalwa ongazisebenzisa ukunceda wena ukwazi ukumelana nonxinzelelo ongazisebenzisa kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BREATHE"
msgstr "PHEFUMLA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Breathe slowly. Pause.\n"
"\n"
"Before you say anything, slowly breathe in and out five times. It will calm you, and give you a chance to think."
msgstr ""
"Phefumla ngokucothayo. Yima.\n"
"\n"
"Ngaphambi kokuba uthethe nantoni na, ngokucothayo phefumla uphinde uwukhuphe izihlandlo ezintlanu. Loo nto iya kukwenza uzole, kwaye ikunike ithuba lokucinga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHARE"
msgstr "YABELANANI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Share how you feel.\n"
"\n"
"This is hard. Many of us were told not to cry, or show our feelings to our children. But take a deep breath and calmly tell them how you feel. They will understand better, and also learn from you how to deal with stress."
msgstr ""
"Yabelana ngendlela oziva ngayo.\n"
"\n"
"Lento inzima. Uninzi lwethu lwaxelelwa ukuba lungakhali, okanye lubonise abantwana indlela esiva ngayo. Kodwa ungaphefumla nzulu ngokuzolileyo kwaye ubaxelele indlela oziva ngayo. Baya kuqonda ngcono, kwaye bafunde kuwe indlela yokuhlangabezana kunye noxinzelelo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHOW"
msgstr "BONISA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Show them you care.\n"
"\n"
"This is also hard! Stress makes us focus on ourselves. But our teens need our support. Ask them how they feel. Listen to them and comfort them. Try a hug or say \"I understand\". It can change everything."
msgstr ""
"Babonise uyakhathala\n"
"\n"
"Nale inzima! Uxinzelelo lwenza ukuba sinike ingqalelo kwiziqu zethu. Kodwa abantwana bethu abafikisayo bayayidinga inkxaso yethu. Babuze indlela abaziva ngayo. Mamela kubo kwaye ubathuthuzele. Zama ubanga okanye uthi ‘Ndiyaqonda’. Ingatshintsha yonke into."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEEK"
msgstr "FUNA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Seek the positive.\n"
"\n"
"Can you and your teen think about ideas that might help? Can you do something positive together to take your mind off the stress?"
msgstr ""
"Funa okulungileyo.\n"
"\n"
"Ungakwazi wena nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ukucinga ngezinto ezinokuba luncedo? Ningakwazi ukwenza into elungileyo nobabini ukususa iingqondo zenu kuxinzelelo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Here is your home activity for this week:\n"
"\n"
"Whenever you are feeling stressed or upset with your teen, take five breaths in and out before you react.\n"
"\n"
"And when you're both calm, share with each other how you feel."
msgstr ""
"Nanku umsebenzi wakho wale veki:\n"
"\n"
"Nanini xa uziva unoxinzelelo okanye ukhathazekile ngomntwana wakho osafikisayo, phefumla kahlanu ngaphakathi nangaphandle, phambi kokuthatha amanyatelo.\n"
"\n"
"Kwaye xa nobabini ninomoya ozolileyo, nabelane ngendlela omnye nomnye aziva ngayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember to:** \n"
"\n"
"😮‍💨 BREATHE: take five breaths in and out before you react\n"
"🤝🏾 SHARE: when you're both calm, share with your teen how you feel\n"
"💙 SHOW: ask them how they feel to show you care\n"
"🔍 SEEK: find something positive in this situation together"
msgstr ""
"**Khumbula uku:**\n"
"\n"
"😮‍💨 PHEFUMLA: phefumla kahlanu ngaphakathi nangaphandle phambi kokuba uphendule\n"
"🤝🏾 YABELANA: xa nobabini nizolile, yabelanani wena nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ngohlobo oziva ngalo\n"
"💙 BONISA: babuze ukuba baziva njani ukubonisa ukuba uyakhathala\n"
"🔍 FUNA: fumanani into elungileyo kwesisimo kunye"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you respond calmly with your teen this week?"
msgstr "Ungakwazi ukuphendula uzolile umntwana wakho ofikisayo kuleveki?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great! Staying calm will help you and your family."
msgstr "Kulungile! Ukuhlala uzolile kuzakunceda wena kunye nosapho lwakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s a good start. When you are stressed, remember to take a few deep breaths, it will make it easier to respond calmly."
msgstr "Eso sisiqalo esilungileyo. Xa unoxinzelelo, khumbula ukuphefumla kancinci, lonto izakwenza kubelula ukuphendula ngokuzolileyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I understand, sometimes we just don’t have capacity. Try to keep spending time with your teen - whenever you are ready you can practise responding calmly together."
msgstr "Ndiyayiqonda, ngamanye amaxesha asinawo umthamo. Zama uqhubeke uchitha ixesha nomntana wakho ofikisayo - naninina ulungele ungazilungiselela uphendula ngokuzolileyo kunye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, when we practice responding calmly and sharing how we feel, our teens learn to do the same. This skill will help them their whole life!"
msgstr "Khumbula, xa sizama ukuphendula zolileyo kwaye sabelane ngendlela esiziva ngayo, abantwana bethu abafikisayo bafunda ukwenza ngokufanayo. Esisakhono siyakubanceda ubomu babo bonke!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name learned to stay calm from her mother"
msgstr "Mamela indlela u@data.characters.media_daughter_1.name afunde ngayo ukuhlala ezolile kumama wakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Whenever I would do something wrong, my mother would get so angry at me and beat me. She would not even listen to me and I would get so angry as well at her and everyone else.\n"
"\n"
"Now, when she gets angry, she first takes a few deep breaths before she responds. It makes everyone calm down instead of causing a big fight.\n"
"\n"
"It really helped me at home and at school. Now, when I feel really angry or stressed, I also take deep breaths like my mother does. I feel like a different person."
msgstr ""
"Naninina ndisenza into engalunganga, umama wam uye abenomsindo kakhulu kum kwaye andibethe. Uye angakwazi nokundimamela kwaye ndiye ndibenomsindo kakhulu kuye nakwabanye abantu.\n"
"\n"
"Ngoku, xa enomsindo uye aphefumle kambalwa kuqala phambi kokuba aphendule. Lonto yenza wonke umntu abenomoya ozolileyo endaweni yokubangela umlo omkhulu.\n"
"\n"
"Indincedile nyhani lonto ekhaya kunye nasesikolweni, ngoku, xana ndiziva ndinomsindo nyani okanye ndinoxinzelelo, Nam ndiye ndiphefumle ngohlobo umama wam enza ngalo. Ndingumntu owohlukileyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr "Wenze kakuhle ngokuthatha ixesha lesiqu sakho namhlanje. 🎉"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr "Nali ushicilelo olufutshane elizokunceda wehlise ngaphambi kokuba uhambe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
"Xa yonke into ivakala ingathi iyamoshakala Kwaye awukwazi ukuzinceda uvele unyuse ilizwi Xa zonke iinzingo ziqala Khumbula ukuba ungenza ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sehlise kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba andinakuthanda ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Yima, ungabala uyokutsho ku 10 Dlala umdlalo okanye wenze into emnandi Ungafowunela umhlobo, umntu onokumchazela ingxaki Khumbula ayinguwe wedwa\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi \n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsalaa umoya Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsalaa umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi"

